data.description: Stunning ranch style home with open floor plan in highly sought after Edgewater Community. Amenities and luxury galore! Community includes Pristine Golf Course, Marina/Docks, Tennis Courts, Pool, and Walking Trails! Home has been updated including landscaping for added curb appeal, enclosed back porch + Concrete patio. Home welcomes you in past covered front porch into entryway and open living space. Living room has coffered ceilings and french door leading to enclosed porch creating tons of natural light. Gourmet bright kitchen has granite countertops, recessed lighting, SS appliances and island seating for additional space plus tons of cabinets & full pantry for storage. Primary bedroom w/ ensuite has walk-in closet & stand-up shower. 2 additional bedrooms & full hall bath perfect for guests. Backyard w/ patio ideal for grilling looks out into wooded area for perfect privacy. Truly a peaceful home in great neighborhood. A MUST SEE!
